                                <li>3.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Applicants are requested to ensure that the following documents are prepared and
                                    readily available before initiating the proposal submission process:
                                    
                                    <div class="stage-subsection">
                                        <div class="stage-heading">1st Stage Proposal Submission</div>
                                        <ul class="aligned-list">
