                        <div class="what-to-expect-content">

                            <!-- IGSTC Industrial Fellowship Section -->
                            <div class="igstc-logo" style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                                <img src="{!URLFOR($Resource.Logo)}" alt="IGSTC Logo"
                                    style="height: 60px; width: auto; display: inline-block;" />
                            </div>
                            <h4 style="text-align: center; margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                                IGSTC Industrial Fellowship
                            </h4>

                            <h5 style="text-align: center;">What to Expect Before You Start Your Application</h5>
                            <p style="color: red;"><em><b>*Kindly note below is a guideline for you to be prepared
                                        before starting the
                                        application. It gives a symbolic representation of different sections of the
                                        application. But the most up-to-date information will be available inside
                                        the
                                        various sections of the application portal.</b></em></p>

                            <p>Applying for the IGSTC fellowship is a structured, multi-step process. To ensure a
                                smooth
                                experience, please familiarise yourself following before you begin:</p>

                            <h5>1. Registration (First Step)</h5>
                            <p>Before starting the application, you must register/login via the IGSTC portal:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Click on “Sign Up” if you are a new user
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Provide your email ID and create a password
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Verify using captcha and complete registration
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Existing users can directly “Sign In”
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    In case of issues, use “Forgot Password” or “Contact Support”
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>2. Application Structure</h5>
                            <p>The application is divided into multiple sections that must be completed
                                sequentially:
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Basic Details
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Personal Information
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Parent Organisation Details
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Education Details
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Employment Details
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Achievements
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Host Organisation Details
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Project Details
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Attachments
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Final Review &amp; Submission
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>3. Documents You Should Keep Ready</h5>
                            <p>Prepare the following documents in advance (PDF format, <b>max size: 1 MB each</b>):
                            </p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Consent Letter from the Host Organization
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    NOC from the Head of the institution: NOC Format
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Recommendation letter from the mentor at parent organisation
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Two reference letters from established researchers in the field for PDIF
                                    applicants
                                    not having affiliation with an institution
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Proof of Date of Birth (Scan copy of Passport/ Aadhar Card)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Proof of Education Qualifications arranged in reverse chronological order
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Proof of Employment
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Passport size photo in jpg/jpeg with the following size limits (30 Kb - max 500
                                    Kb)
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>4. Content Preparation (Important)</h5>
                            <p>Several sections require detailed write-ups. It is strongly recommended to:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Avoid formatting issues in the online editor
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Stay within character limits:
                                    <ul>
                                        <li> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle text-success"
                                                style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                            Abstract (Max ~500 characters without space)
                                        </li>
                                        <li> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle text-success"
                                                style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                            Statement of Purpose (Max ~1200 characters without space)
                                        </li>
                                        <li> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle text-success"
                                                style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                            Work Plan (Max ~2000 characters without space)
                                        </li>
                                        <li> <i class="fa-regular fa-circle text-success"
                                                style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                            Organisation Portfolio (Max ~250 characters without space)
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>5. Academic &amp; Professional Details</h5>
                            <p>Be ready with:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Degrees in reverse chronological order (PhD first)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    CGPA/Percentage (with scale clearly mentioned)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Thesis details (title, supervisor, duration)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Employment history (latest first)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Details of ongoing research/project
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>6. Project Information Requirements</h5>
                            <p>You will need to clearly define:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Problem statement and motivation
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Objectives (max 4)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Detailed work plan (with timelines)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Expected outcomes (max 6)
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <p>Ensure clarity, feasibility, and alignment with the fellowship goals.</p>

                            <h5>7. Host &amp; Parent Organisation Details</h5>
                            <p>Keep the following handy:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Organisation name, address, and country
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Mentor details (Name, designation, contact info)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Brief portfolio of both organisations
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>8. Eligibility &amp; Key Checks</h5>
                            <p>Before starting:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Ensure you meet age and eligibility criteria
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Confirm PhD status (awarded/submitted)
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Verify institutional affiliation requirements
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>9. Technical Tips</h5>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Use a <b>stable internet connection</b>
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Preferred browsers: Chrome / Firefox
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    If the portal hangs, try: <b>Ctrl + Shift + R (Hard Refresh)</b>
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Save progress frequently
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Contact Support or Raise a Ticket in case of any issues, which would be
                                    responded/resolved in 48 hrs.
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>10. Final Submission</h5>
                            <p>Before submitting:</p>
                            <ul>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Review all sections carefully
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Ensure all documents are uploaded
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Confirm declaration and signature
                                </li>
                                <li> <i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-success"
                                        style="font-size: 8px; margin-top: 6px; margin-right: 12px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
                                    Once submitted, changes may not be allowed
                                </li>
                            </ul>

                            <h5>11. Time Commitment</h5>
                            <p>Completing the application may take 2–4 hours, depending on preparedness.</p>

                            <h5>Pro Tip</h5>
                            <p>Applicants who prepare all documents and content in advance complete the application
                                <b>3x faster and with fewer errors</b>.
                            </p>

                        </div>

                        <div class="what-to-expect-popup-buttons">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary" ng-click="closeWhatToExpectPopup()">
                                Close
                            </button>
                        </div>

